reviewText: I anticipated that this release would be just what it is:  a variety type show with wrap-arounds starring W&G.;  Fun stuff to be sure, but make no mistake:  this is NOT a new set of adventures with our pals.While it's great to have them back, it is a far cry from previous releases.By all means; if you are a huge fan (as we are) pick this up and enjoy - and maybe even learn something.  Just don't bring any expectations from previous adventures.
summary: Wallace & Gromit are back....well, sort of....
